cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "Clinical Code Discovery (clinicalcodes.uk)"
abstract: >-
  A multi-source pipeline that discovers candidate clinical codes
  (SNOMED CT, ICD-10, OPCS-4) via parallel retrievers across UK
  clinical vocabularies, enriches them through UMLS-based synonym
  expansion, and supports validation through per-code LLM scoring
  (Claude Haiku 4.5) and a human review gate. Output format is
  compatible with OpenCodelists.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Ramirez
    given-names: Carlos
    affiliation: "University of Cambridge (PACE)"
repository-code: "https://github.com/carlos-ramblox/nice-clinical-codes"
url: "https://clinicalcodes.uk"
license: Apache-2.0
keywords:
  - clinical codes
  - codelist generation
  - SNOMED CT
